list.comment:
Added put function for Progress and a few other small changes throughout the code including fixing delete errors, and normal style changes.
Issue: When adding an update to Progress through the PUT function, an error is thrown stating that "age must be an array but is of type int in document". Age is in the document as a Number, for the record. Attempting to resolve the issue again.
